items.title: Boorum & Pease Record/Account Book  Journal Rule  Blue  300 Pages  12 1/8 x 7 5/8
items.description: Keep records in timeless style with the Boorum & Pease Record Account Book. Its numbered pages  table of contents and an integrated ribbon ensure easy navigation. Sewn-in sheets prevent loose pages and show evidence of tampering. The Smyth-sewn construction lies flat to let you read from margin to margin  and premium  acid-free paper offers an exceptional way to preserve information. This Boorum & Pease journal features 33 lines per page  no units  a table of contents page and a blue canvas cover. Its red and blue journal rulings are waterproof and permanent.
